MACD Zero Line Description:

Buy, MACD in Bullish Territory, The MACD is currently positioned above the zero line. This usually indicates that the asset's short-term momentum is outpacing its long-term momentum. Historically, when MACD remains above the zero line for extended periods, it can signal a sustained bullish phase.
